{
  "id": "adv_card_ngs_05_02",
  "title": "伊吹渚",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ダイエットの基本は、やっぱり運動と食事管理だ",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "ですよね、分かってはいるんですけど……",
      "startTime": 4.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "ダイエットしてるの、恥ずかしくて\nみんなに言えないんです",
      "startTime": 10.9872764023,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "だから、始めるきっかけが掴めなくて……",
      "startTime": 13.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "俺に任せてくれ。気付かれないようにしてみせる",
      "startTime": 16.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "渚は食事の時間をみんなとずらそう\nトレーニングにも、ダイエット向けのものを組み込む",
      "startTime": 23.4433333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "何から何まですみません……",
      "startTime": 26.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "いいんだ。そのかわりに\n夏フェスでは最高のステージを見せてくれ",
      "startTime": 31.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　ここまでしてもらって\nダイエットに失敗するなんて許されません！",
      "startTime": 36.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "必ず成功させて\nアイドルボディを手に入れてみせます！",
      "startTime": 40.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、頼むぞ。時間もないし早速始めよう\nまずはプランク20回を3セットだ",
      "startTime": 47.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、5……10セットやります！",
      "startTime": 50.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "え？　それはやり過ぎなんじゃ……\n初日だし、今日は軽めにしといた方が",
      "startTime": 56.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんはまだ分かってません！\nその優しさが時に人を傷つけるんですよー",
      "startTime": 62.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "分かった分かった。じゃあ始めよう",
      "startTime": 66.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　いーち、にーい、さーん……",
      "startTime": 69.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（そうは言っても実際、渚のスタイルは悪くない）",
      "startTime": 77.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（要は気持ちの問題だ。自信さえつけば変わるはずだ）\n（俺は体を壊さないように目を配っておこう）",
      "startTime": 86.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "ふん、ふん、ふん！\nふぅ、これで12セット目！",
      "startTime": 93.6191788195,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "――って、もうそんなに！？\n渚、ペースが速過ぎる。抑えて！",
      "startTime": 99.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "え？　あっ、気付いたらもうこんなに……",
      "startTime": 102.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "頑張らなきゃって思ってたら\nつい夢中になっちゃいました",
      "startTime": 108.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "怖いくらい速かったぞ\n渚の残像が見えた気がする……",
      "startTime": 113.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02-ngs013.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、次は何をしましょう？",
      "startTime": 115.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "いや、さすがに12セットの後だし\n少し休んだ方がいい",
      "startTime": 121.7469760132,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02-ngs014.m4a",
      "text": "何を言ってるんですか！\nフェスまであと二週間もないんですよ！？",
      "startTime": 125.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02-ngs015.m4a",
      "text": "もし、計量で失格になったら、どうするんですか！？",
      "startTime": 128.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "落ち着いてくれ。アイドルに計量するルールはないから\nボクサーじゃないんだし",
      "startTime": 136.5258856896,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02-ngs016.m4a",
      "text": "とにかく次の指示をお願いします！",
      "startTime": 138.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "分かったよ\nじゃあ、クランチ10回を2セット……",
      "startTime": 142.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02-ngs017.m4a",
      "text": "10セットです！　お腹周りは特に大事ですから！",
      "startTime": 145.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "変なスイッチ入っちゃったな……\n無理はするなよ",
      "startTime": 152.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02-ngs018.m4a",
      "text": "いきます！　1、2、3、4、5、6――",
      "startTime": 154.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "速い！　渚、速いから！　もっと抑えて！",
      "startTime": 158.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 162.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "よし、出来たぞ。栄養士さんに聞いて作った\nダイエットメニューだ",
      "startTime": 166.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02-ngs019.m4a",
      "text": "ゆで野菜に、鶏のささみの湯引き……\nご飯は玄米なんですね",
      "startTime": 171.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02-koh018.m4a",
      "text": "高たんぱく、低脂質だよ\nこっちの海藻サラダも味付けにオイルは使ってない",
      "startTime": 176.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02-ngs020.m4a",
      "text": "どれも美味しそうです\n{user}さんも同じメニューなんですか？",
      "startTime": 182.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02-koh019.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、一緒に頑張ってる人がそばにいたら\n挫折しにくいと思って",
      "startTime": 188.4343333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02-ngs021.m4a",
      "text": "なんだか、すみません……私のせいで",
      "startTime": 190.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02-koh020.m4a",
      "text": "気にすることはないよ\nさぁ、お腹空いてるだろう。食べてくれ",
      "startTime": 195.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
