      "text": "じゃあ、おかわりを――ってダメです！",
      "startTime": 209.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02-ngs024.m4a",
      "text": "もう、{user}さん！\n私を甘やかすの禁止です！",
      "startTime": 215.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02-koh022.m4a",
      "text": "はいはい、でも、必要な栄養はとってくれよ\nステージで踊る体力まで落としたら意味がないぞ",
      "startTime": 222.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02-ngs025.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　それはもちろん分かってます\nあくまで夏フェスを成功させるのが目標ですから",
      "startTime": 227.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_05_02-ngs026.m4a",
      "text": "ああ～鶏のささみ、もうなくなっちゃった……\nもっと噛み締めて食べれば良かった……",
      "startTime": 235.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
